      "cvrf:Note": [
        {
          "#text": "A Stack-based Buffer Overflow vulnerability [CWE-121] in FortiManager fgtupdates service may allow a remote unauthenticated attacker to execute unauthorized commands via crafted requests, if the service is enabled. The success of the attack depends on the ability to bypass the stack protection mechanisms.",
